    <title>hexo主题skapp添加valine评论系统方法</title>
    <link href="https://www.nohapa.com/post/f8df58f6.html"/>
    <id>https://www.nohapa.com/post/f8df58f6.html</id>
    <published>2017-12-28T15:25:36.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-12-28T16:24:33.718Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h1><p>经过了解hexo+github的强大之处后。本网站决定抛弃臃肿的Java框架和收费的服务器，采用hexo+github生成的静态文件来重新搭建网站。</p><p>在纠结于使用哪个评论系统的时候，发现了valine这个极简的评论系统。</p><p>官网没有介绍skapp主题的添加方法。</p><p>所以写此教程来记录一下添加的方法，避免少踩坑，浪费时间。</p><h2 id="使用方法"><a href="#使用方法" class="headerlink" title="使用方法"></a>使用方法</h2><p>1、首先登录valine的官网<a href="https://valine.js.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://valine.js.org</a></p><p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2017/12/28/zMNTg.png" alt="valine1"></p><ul><li><p>按照官网提供的方法获取appid和appkey</p></li><li><p>npm安装——npm install valine –save</p></li></ul><p>2、根目录_config.yml添加如下代码（非主题里的_config.yml）</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Valine comments https://valine.js.org</span><br><span class="line">valine:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  appid: 你的appid</span><br><span class="line">  appkey: 你的appkey</span><br><span class="line">  notify: false </span><br><span class="line">  verify: false</span><br><span class="line">  pageSize: 10</span><br><span class="line">  avatar: mm</span><br><span class="line">  placeholder: Just go go</span><br><span class="line">  guest_info: nick,mail,link</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>3、打开xxx\themes\hexo-theme-skapp\layout_partial\common下的comment.swig，添加如下代码</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% if page.comments &amp;&amp; config.valine %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"//cdn1.lncld.net/static/js/3.0.4/av-min.js"</span>&gt;</span><span class="undefined"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"//unpkg.com/valine/dist/Valine.min.js"</span>&gt;</span><span class="undefined"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="undefined"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined">var GUEST_INFO = ['nick','mail','link'];</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined">var guest_info = '&#123;&#123; config.valine.guest_info &#125;&#125;'.split(',').filter(function(item)&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined">return GUEST_INFO.indexOf(item) -1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined">&#125;);</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined">var notify = '&#123;&#123; config.valine.notify &#125;&#125;' == true;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined">var verify = '&#123;&#123; config.valine.verify &#125;&#125;' == true;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined">new Valine(&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined">el: '#comments',</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined">notify: notify,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined">verify: verify,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined">appId: '&#123;&#123; config.valine.appid &#125;&#125;',</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined">appKey: '&#123;&#123; config.valine.appkey &#125;&#125;',</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined">placeholder: '&#123;&#123; config.valine.placeholder &#125;&#125;',</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined">pageSize: '&#123;&#123; config.valine.pageSize &#125;&#125;',</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined">avatar: '&#123;&#123; config.valine.avatar &#125;&#125;',</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined">&#125;);</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="undefined">  </span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endif %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>4、打开xxx\themes\hexo-theme-skapp\layout_partial\post下的main.swig，添加如下代码（紧接着上一个endif）</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% if page.comments &amp;&amp; config.valine %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">br</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">"comments"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endif %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>5、hexo g  hexo s 启动本地服务器后检查是否成功（自己测试一下）。最后hexo d同步至github</p><p>6、其他一些样式配置请看官网</p><p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2017/12/28/zMwfs.png" alt="配置成功"></p>]]></content>
    
